headline: Dow Jones Futures: Will Apple, Techs Rally On Big Trump Tariff Exemption? Palantir Leads 7 Stocks To Watch
summary: The market whipsawed higher last week. Apple and electronics just won a big tariff exemption, which could buoy techs Monday.. Palantir leads stocks setting up.
